Requires a 404.php and a symbolic link to the index.php file in the webroot.

Requires the following rewrites:

    RewriteEngine on
    RewriteBase /
    
    RewriteRule ^([0-9]{4})/([0-9]{2})/([0-9]{2})/([a-z\-]+)/$ /index.php?year=$1&month=$2&day=$3&slug=$4 [L]
    RewriteRule ^([0-9]{4})/([0-9]{2})/$ /index.php?year=$1&month=$2 [L]
